column12: Honestly, who gives a pop quiz on the day of the midterm? It is ridiculous when everyone is studying for it. Otherwise, lecture is boring and definitely not helpful. Your TA is most helpful, and all the quizzes in TA section, at least this semester, is all multiple choice. Overall, it isn't really difficult material.

He is the worst teacher ever!!! The midterm was the worst.  There was a question on it that was the same as one on a practice midterm, and the right answer on the practice midterm wasn't the same as the correct answer on the real midterm, so people complained, and he didn't care to do anything.  I hate him!
Unclear during lecutres; does not respond to student e-mails.  TA is your instructor, so hope you get a good one.

He barely says anything worth noting in the lectures. For the conflict midterm he did all essay when the actual midterm was all multiple choice. Not only that, but one of the 16 essays on the midterm counted for half the exam. He isn't very fair, and I think you would get more out of engaging with the book rather than going to lecture. what a waste

Gottheil is the worst teacher ever.   My dad had him in 1970 when he was a socialist.  Fred will be 79 this year.  He's old and needs to quit teaching.  His tests are awful and he's not fun and just plain annoying when he clicks and talks about fish and hat factories.
THIS MAN IS THE DEVIL INCARNATE
This man is the root of all evil
